		"<!--<p><em>Warning: this site contains graphic violence.</em></p>-->",
		"<p>At last, Diablo IV! It's a dream come true to not only be able to build the official website, but also a rare opportunity to be involved from the very beginning with a brand new project. This was my first time designing the system architecture for a new site of this stature.</p>",
		"<p>The site's front end is entirely in React and uses the <a class=\"Link\" href=\"https://nextjs.org\">Next.js</a> framework, which we chose to easily enable server-side rendering. Our styles are primarily done using <a class=\"Link\" href=\"https://tailwindcss.com\">Tailwind</a>, which I think is impeccably designed, and its creator noticed and had <a class=\"Link\" href=\"https://twitter.com/adamwathan/status/1190421615068270592\">some very kind words</a> for us on Twitter.",
